  abstract  = "Abstract Long-term growth in developing countries has been
               explained in four frameworks: ?extractive colonial institutions?
               (Acemoglu et al., 2001), ?colonial legal origin? (La Porta et
               al., 2004), ?geography? (Gallup et al., 1998) and ?colonial
